"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934043-Olympic-Hockey-Netherlands-Germany-brawl\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The final of theOlympicmen's hockey erupted into a mass brawl on Thursday after Dutch player Duco Telgenkamp celebrated scoring the winning goal by shushing in the face of the German goalkeeper.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7223946036587299, \"rank\": 0.37241988475396953, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duco\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Duco\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duco\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.5827475607888825, \"rank\": 0.7157003406884177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the scoreline tied at 1-1 at the end of regulation time, the match went to a shootout to decide who picked up the gold medals.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Netherlands took an early lead thanks to the heroics of goalkeeper Pirmin Blaak, leaving Telgenkamp with a chance to seal the victory with his shot.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999973824742, \"rank\": 2.286623307686392e-09, \"text\": \"The Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pirmin_Blaak\", \"score\": 0.9999999745145945, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pirmin Blaak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pirmin_Blaak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pirmin_Blaak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old duly converted, chipping the ball over the outstretched arm of the German keeper Jean-Paul Danneberg.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.5827475607888825, \"rank\": 0.7157003406884177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Dutch players stormed over to celebrate, Telgenkamp stoked the fires, putting his finger to his lips and shushing his rival at close quarters.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7223946036587299, \"rank\": 0.37241988475396953, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A handful of the German players took issue with Telgenkamp's gloating with Niklas Wellen rushing into a huddle of celebrating Dutch players in an attempt to enact revenge.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.5827475607888825, \"rank\": 0.7157003406884177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niklas_Wellen\", \"score\": 0.9999997747816249, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Niklas Wellen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niklas_Wellen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niklas_Wellen\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7223946036587299, \"rank\": 0.37241988475396953, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was intercepted by some of the agitator's team-mates, and a brawl commenced.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the post-match press conference, after the chaos had subsided, Telgenkamp explained that his unsportsmanlike actions were a reaction to Danneberg's comments.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The German goalkeeper insinuated that the Dutch were afraid to face his team.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.5827475607888825, \"rank\": 0.7157003406884177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7223946036587299, \"rank\": 0.37241988475396953, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It all kicked off after the Netherlands won gold in the Hockey against Germany ?\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9955957409558389, \"rank\": 0.004423741617415043, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999917522249, \"rank\": 7.730187516275531e-08, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"??????????\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"?#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/OBMBNv4tkc    Explaining himself, Telgenkamp cut a fine line between apologising for and justifying his actions.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In hindsight, I should not have gone to him.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I regret that.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also apologise,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I should have let it go and it wasn't very smart.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it's also a bit the nature of the beast.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can be very cool-headed, but I can also let myself go.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is that part of it?\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He affected me personally.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports are not business, it does not take much to be provoked.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how I go into the match.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt a bit offended.\\\"\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Meanwhile, the mood in the German camp was one of disappointment and frustration.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.5827475607888825, \"rank\": 0.7157003406884177, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forward Christopher Ruhr insisted that his team deserved to win the game and was dissatisfied with his silver medal.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2233, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruhr\", \"score\": 0.9998706578506912, \"rank\": 0.0001292112934895207, \"text\": \"Ruhr\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruhr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruhr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We deserved to win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an incredibly close match that came down to the shoot-out,\\\" he complained.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Dutch team had the luck today, but our overall performance was strong.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7223946036587299, \"rank\": 0.37241988475396953, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it is phenomenal that we made it to two finals at major sports events and won major knockout games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.867369536001957e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2821, \"end\": 2834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.867369536001957e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"